art blir utnyttet, og at noen tjener penger p\u00e5 \u00e5 selge kroppsdeler som eggceller og s\u00e6d, sier Sunde.", "Sunde understreker at det \u00e5 f\u00e5 legehjelp til \u00e5 bli gravid ikke kan v\u00e6re plan A, men en n\u00f8dl\u00f8sning."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a43c46c08c183b394c801c3c824e55040a25df9214c428c0ff1703d38051f57e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-08-11T21:13:52.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "NTNU-professor Arne Sunde mener at empatisurrogati b\u00f8r tillates."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2138662.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/gravid"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8a578379569a587b77f70361ee43fb7d86c9ca9f.jpg?596ef0cd"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Ja til surrogati i Norge -adressa.no", "Empatisurrogati", "Kynisk fertilitetsindustri"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "8a578379569a587b77f70361ee43fb7d86c9ca9f"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "gemini"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["tilby", "empatisurrogati", "hjelp", "kynisk fertilitetsindustri", "surrogati"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["olavs hospital", "nederland og england", "fertilitetsklinikken", "st. olavs hospital"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["danmark", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "arne sunde"}, {"field": "kw-t